OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome sunny
OL,6,Fspells during the evening, but mostly
OL,7,Fcloudy overnight and should remain
OL,8,Fdry. Northeasterly winds increasing
OL,9,Fovernight, becoming breezy especially
OL,10,Falong the coast. Feeling cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA cloudy start to Sunday,
OL,13,Fperhaps some light morning rain across
OL,14,Fsouth Essex. Brighter spells then
OL,15,Fdeveloping during the early evening.
OL,16,FFeeling cool in the brisk
OL,17,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
