OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,6,Fband clears south Monday afternoon,
OL,7,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Cloudier
OL,8,FTuesday with outbreaks of rain late
OL,9,Fon. Wednesday starts off dry with
OL,10,Fheavy showers developing later.
